project_descr: Integrated conservation of priority clobal significant migratory wetlands habitat:demonstration on 3 sites

outputs.output_descr: the proposed project will establish the basis for the development and testing of an integrated and participatory apporach to the conservation and sustainable use of biological diversity in 3 priority wetland sites. the three sties lie along two globally significant migratory flyways and each enables the porject to demonstrate solutions to different issues affecting Kazakhstan's wetland biodirversity resources. In doing so it wll assist the government  to meet its commitments under the Ramsar Convention, due to be signed in 2004
